  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Marketing & Growth Rockstar",
  "description": "<p><strong>Tired of the 9–5 grind with no growth?</strong> Euphoria Organization is looking for ambitious, outgoing individuals who are ready to build a real career, not just a job. No prior experience? No problem — we value energy, drive, and a growth mindset above all else.</p><p><strong>Why Join Us:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Fast-Track Career:</strong> Achieve promotions based on performance, not tenure.</p></li><li><p><strong>Uncapped Earnings:</strong> Your income grows with your effort.</p></li><li><p><strong>1-to-1 Mentorship:</strong> Personalized coaching to help you succeed.</p></li><li><p><strong>Team Culture:</strong> Fun, supportive, non-toxic environment where wins are celebrated.</p></li><li><p><strong>Skill Development:</strong> Training in marketing, leadership, and communication.</p></li><li><p><strong>Performance-Based Travel:</strong> Network and explore regionally as you hit your goals.</p></li></ul><p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Represent major brands face-to-face and build relationships</p></li><li><p>Turn “no” into “yes” through smart, confident communication</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with the team, share ideas, and hit daily targets</p></li></ul><p><strong>Who We’re Looking For:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Outgoing, motivated, and high-energy</p></li><li><p>Hungry to grow a real career</p></li><li><p>Singaporeans or PR only</p></li></ul>",
